data.title: Saovabha Phongsri
data.meta_description: Saovabha Phongsri birth title : Her Royal Highness Princess Saovabha Phongsri was an agnatic half-sister, royal wife and supreme chief queen of King Chulalongkorn of Thailand, and mother of both King Vajiravudh and King Prajadhipok. As in accordance with Thai royal tradition, King Vajiravudh later bestowed on his mother the title of "Her Majesty Queen Mother Sri Bajrindra".
